1. *Stanica* je puna ljudi. (The station is full of people.)
2. Putnici čekaju na *stanici*. (The passengers are waiting at the station.)
3. Naša *stanica* je otvorena od 5 ujutru do 9 uveče. (Our station is open from 5am to 9pm.)
4. *Stanica* je udaljena od grada 3 kilometra. (The station is 3 kilometers away from the city.)
5. *Stanica* je bila zatvorena zbog radova. (The station was closed due to works.)
6. *Stanica* je bila prekrivena snegom. (The station was covered in snow.)